title: Jenny's Sexy Wish: A Futanari Transformation, Breast Expansion, and Lesbian Fantasy
description: Jenny and Faith are perfect for each other, even their deepest, most secret desires complement each other. Too bad they've been too shy or too afraid to take the final step. But that's going to change today. They both have sex on the brain, and they both want to make their desires plain. A little magic ring that Faith found is going to help them, too, because after Jenny takes a leap and makes a deliciously sexy wish, Faith grows a huge new tool that leaves Jenny dripping with desire.
author: Beatrice Evenmorne
